Class AbstractFieldCompetition

  affix.java.effective.field.AbstractFieldCompetition

LongJumpCompetition
abstract class AbstractFieldCompetition
extends java.lang.Object
implements TrackAndFieldCompetition

A general class for holding an array of result objects produced in a TrackAndFieldCompetition. This class is abstract and should only be a holder of general data Inherited classes will define the number of results to handle
